{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were probably some a bit older, but-- And now a new hiding started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to hide away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was quite a surprise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't wait to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so the women were hiding for some time in the cellar, from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I presume it was our liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the moment that they came and took over the occupation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether it was a general liberation of all the war, but liberation of our town-- occupied by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The point that we were in a cellar with the Russian officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not actually leave the cellar yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were talking to this Russian man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he just warned via Pernik that the women have to be very careful, because we have got here an army coming who haven't seen a woman for years-- or for a long period.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it is a very, very ignorant and primitive army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, we're delighted, because we're going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the River Nitra, what is about 30 feet, I can swim it quite easily.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's nothing to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They thought they reached River Volga.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So uninformed were the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you imagine, coming from Russia all the way  to Czechoslovakia, not realizing that where they were physically, actually?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they really thought they were still in Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this was quite a surprise to us, because the German army, on the other hand, were very, very smartly dressed and a very educated lot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here we found these soldiers arriving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But gradually, we moved out, eventually, after some time, to an apartment-- what was also vacant.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
